        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Florentinius Censorinus <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ivus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>et <expan><ex>A</ex><abbr>eli</abbr><ex>a</ex></expan> Brenturia co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>iux</abbr></expan> vivi <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ecerunt</ex></expan> sibi et <expan><abbr>Flore</abbr><ex>ntinio</ex></expan> Floro filio <expan><abbr>car</abbr><ex>issimo</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>eq<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>iti</abbr></expan> <expan><abbr>al</abbr><ex>ae</ex></expan> Com<expan><ex>m</ex><abbr>ag</abbr><ex>enorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>imae</ex></expan> singulari <expan><abbr>stup</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> <note>sic</note> XX <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XL et <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>A</abbr><ex cert="low">elio</ex></expan> <abbr>C</abbr> et Florentinia <lb n="6"/>Florentina <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> LXX
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die A ohne Querhaste, einige Buchstaben sind von der Kursivschrift beinflußt. Ligaturen: Z. 3: AR; Z. 4 und 6: die Zahl XX; Z. 5: TI. Z. 1: Der erste und letzte Buchstabe ragen in den Rahmen hinein, der hierfür abgearbeitet wurde.</p>
            </div>
